construction of approximately 1,500 social housing units in the region. The first phase of the project will bring to being 1,000 housing units, including 402 residential buildings and 54 shops. This phase is estimated to cost about US$ 20.82M. Other projects launched on that particular day include the rehabilitation of the Oum Labouir beach, near Tawarta, and the renovation of the entrance to Dakhla.